    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. This car has been treated as a prized possession since day one, stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring a professional ceramic coating that provides a deep, liquid-like shine on the original factory paint; you will find no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings here. The interior is equally pristine, retaining that distinctive new-car scent. The leather upholstery remains taut and supple with no signs of wear or bolster compression, and the high-gloss trim is free of any micro-scratches. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, with a complete service history from the original selling dealer. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver aids, operates with precision. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the most discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
