      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative example of automotive excellence, maintained in pristine, showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, resulting in a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains entirely unblemished. Offering an investment-grade opportunity for the sophisticated buyer, its mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation are beyond reproach. This is, without compromise, the finest specimen currently available on the market.",
